<div class="text"><h3>Checkout <a href="http://www.hivlegalnetwork.ca/site/comic-no-police-at-overdoses-good-samaritan-drug-overdose-act/?lang=en">this wonderful comic</a>&nbsp;Criminology's Emily van der Meulen was involved in</h3>
</div>

