<li class="biographyListTeaserContentContainer" style="list-style-image:none;list-style-type:none;">
<div>

    <div class="biographyName"><a href="/content/ryerson/criminology/research-and-innovation/research-spotlights/on-point-report.html" title="Emily Van Der Meulen"> Emily Van Der Meulen</a></div>




    <div class="biographyDepartment"><a style="">Department:</a> In early February 2016, Dr. Emily van der Meulen and her research team launched their new report on prison-based needle and syringe programs (PNSPs). The report outlines her multi-year, multi-phase undertaking and includes six recommendations about how PNSPs can be effectively implemented in Canadian federal prisons.</div>
 







    <div class="biographySpecialization"><a style="">Areas of Expertise:</a> Department of Criminology</div> 

